{"tid":2312090,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★神秘白光「閃現」紐約　巨響震撼民房","createTime":"2020-12-04T14:46:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T15:14:12.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"934133f5253032e85a4836f9cc0cc45fe540fb91","tid":2312090,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T14:46:21.000Z","msg":"美國紐約上州大部分區域的上空12月2日出現神秘的「爆炸」，令當地房屋搖晃，窗戶嘎嘎作響。<br />\n<br />\n紐約州中部有居民從2日中午起報警，稱聽到和感受到巨大的爆炸。紐約奧農多加（Onondaga）到約65公里遠的的奧斯威戈（Oswego）再到更遠的麥迪遜（Madison）和奧奈達（Oneida）的居民都感受到震盪。<br />\n<br />\n曾競逐國會議席的候選人米索（Roger Misso）在Twitter上推文，稱置身家中感覺整幢屋都在震動。<br />\n<br />\n&darr;網民在Twitter分享紐約出現白光的片段<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/status/1334283883051937793\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1334283883051937793&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1w3yU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=ca82dd08\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1334283883051937793&h=55c78dfa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/i/status/1334283883051937793</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E8%AA%AA/557219/%E7%A5%9E%E7%A7%98%E7%99%BD%E5%85%89-%E9%96%83%E7%8F%BE-%E7%B4%90%E7%B4%84-%E5%B7%A8%E9%9F%BF%E9%9C%87%E6%92%BC%E6%B0%91%E6%88%BF-%E5%A5%87%E6%99%AF%E9%81%A0%E8%87%B3%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7%E9%83%BD%E5%8F%AF%E7%9C%8B%E8%A6%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25E8%25AA%25AA%2F557219%2F%25E7%25A5%259E%25E7%25A7%2598%25E7%2599%25BD%25E5%2585%2589-%25E9%2596%2583%25E7%258F%25BE-%25E7%25B4%2590%25E7%25B4%2584-%25E5%25B7%25A8%25E9%259F%25BF%25E9%259C%2587%25E6%2592%25BC%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2588%25BF-%25E5%25A5%2587%25E6%2599%25AF%25E9%2581%25A0%25E8%2587%25B3%25E5%258A%25A0%25E6%258B%25BF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2583%25BD%25E5%258F%25AF%25E7%259C%258B%25E8%25A6%258B&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1w3yU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=35aef4e5\" data-auto-link target